1. Description of Projects
ConvertBitmap
  Convert bmp to png files
Heroes
  Main Heroes application
Heroes.Core
  Heroes basic class
Heroes.Core.Battle
  Battle screen, quick battle
Heroes.Core.Castle
  Castle screen
Heroes.Core.Map
  Big map and mini map
Heroes.Core.Remoting
  .Net remoting classes for multiplayer
HeroesServer
  .Net remoting Server application

